{"tid":1785431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"林鄭月娥稱23條立法需審時度勢　首要任務遏止暴力","createTime":"2019-12-16T11:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T11:57:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"79958452ebc0b480e7c2907659a5481828782a2a","tid":1785431,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:06:21.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥向國家主席習近平及總理李克強述職，她傍晚會見傳媒，表示今年述職的背景與往年不同，最近6個月因修例事件而出現動盪，是回歸以來最嚴峻及複雜的局面。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月鄭說，香港經濟發展要重回正軌，要中央大力支持，她有向領導人提出不同經濟領域希望中央未來推出有利措施。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有無就基本法23條立法的壓力，她說維護國家主權和安全是本港憲制責任，23條曾引起爭議，認為要審時度世，目前工作是止暴制亂。"},{"pid":"59ccda7f4cdcb75c780d5200d65e8066013db510","tid":1785431,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"林鄭月娥你幾時死"},{"pid":"58148921365e3d25d886a3c441add6124310ae16","tid":1785431,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"a72e0f81e6d56f1741682c6d909c54ca217c8807","tid":1785431,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12a8c59f3d87072a55b0022d83ba0822ef62b216","tid":1785431,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:10:54.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁厚面皮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBy the way, 借宣傳一下個APP<br />\n<br />\n香港地投票 - 黎投票啦！📊📊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784354\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784354</a>"},{"pid":"38c213a15442f00fb38cddfc2a93849b60332b49","tid":1785431,"uid":175346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a7f190a4dc41cf59796278dab2f86f68a44e1464","tid":1785431,"uid":254594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a72e0f81e6d56f1741682c6d909c54ca217c8807","tid":1785431,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:09:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:13:10.000Z","msg":"一